definitions.definition: A person (especially a farmer ) of relatively recent Central or Eastern European peasant extraction.
A person who is foolish , stupid , oafish , wild , impetuous , or stubborn .

main_definition: ( US , slang ) A person (especially a farmer ) of relatively recent Central or Eastern European peasant extraction.
secondary_definitions: ( US , slang , sometimes derogatory ) A person who is foolish , stupid , oafish , wild , impetuous , or stubborn .
